{
  "_doc": "Blacklist for build-landing.mjs aggregator. Filters out generic non-AI noise that crowds out real AI signal due to high star counts. Keep conservative — only add entries that are observably crowding out AI items, not opinions.",
  "_added": "2026-05-07 (TrendRadar cherry-pick #2)",
  "version": 1,
